{"article_id":"xCOrBXuwv32sbA62","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"President Trump on Monday accused former FBI Director James Comey of having illegally leaked classified material , on the heels of a report","depth":6},{"id":1,"text":"saying","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"more than half the memos","depth":10},{"id":3,"text":"Comey wrote","depth":10},{"id":4,"text":"detailing Russia-related conversations with the president","depth":9},{"id":5,"text":"contained such information .","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"The Hill ,","depth":9},{"id":7,"text":"quoting \" officials familiar with the documents , \"","depth":9},{"id":8,"text":"reported overnight","depth":8},{"id":9,"text":"that Comey penned a total of seven memos","depth":9},{"id":10,"text":"describing his talks with Trump on the Russia case earlier this year -","depth":9},{"id":11,"text":"and four of them had markings","depth":9},{"id":12,"text":"indicating","depth":10},{"id":13,"text":"they contained classified material at the \" secret \" or \" confidential \" level .","depth":10},{"id":14,"text":"According to the report ,","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"the memos recently were shown to Congress","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"-- and the FBI claimed","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"they were all government documents ,","depth":9},{"id":18,"text":"despite Comey ' s description of his notes as personal .","depth":9},{"id":19,"text":"\" James Comey leaked CLASSIFIED INFORMATION to the media .","depth":6},{"id":20,"text":"That is so illegal ! \"","depth":6},{"id":21,"text":"the president tweeted .","depth":5},{"id":22,"text":"The claims in The Hill","depth":5},{"id":23,"text":"regarding Comey ' s memos","depth":5},{"id":24,"text":"are a throwback to the same kind of allegations against former Democratic presidential candidate Hillary Clinton ,","depth":5},{"id":25,"text":"whom Comey ' s team investigated","depth":6},{"id":26,"text":"for mishandling classified material on her private server and email .","depth":6},{"id":27,"text":"The report comes","depth":5},{"id":28,"text":"as Trump and his family separately are grappling with a New York Times report","depth":6},{"id":29,"text":"that Donald Trump Jr. and other members of the president ' s inner circle met last summer with a Russian lawyer with the expectation","depth":8},{"id":30,"text":"of getting \" damaging information \" on Clinton","depth":8},{"id":31,"text":"- information","depth":8},{"id":32,"text":"that ,","depth":10},{"id":33,"text":"according to Trump ' s son ,","depth":10},{"id":34,"text":"did not materialize .","depth":9},{"id":35,"text":"A special counsel has been tasked with investigating Russian meddling in the campaign and possible collusion with Trump associates ,","depth":5},{"id":36,"text":"ever since Trump fired Comey earlier this year .","depth":5},{"id":37,"text":"On the heels of that firing , Comey first admitted in congressional testimony","depth":5},{"id":38,"text":"that he had used an old friend at Columbia University","depth":6},{"id":39,"text":"to get his notes leaked to The New York Times about his discussions with Trump .","depth":6},{"id":40,"text":"But","depth":7},{"id":41,"text":"asked about the latest claims ,","depth":7},{"id":42,"text":"Columbia University professor Daniel Richman","depth":9},{"id":43,"text":"-- the Comey friend","depth":10},{"id":44,"text":"who leaked part of one memo to The New York Times --","depth":10},{"id":45,"text":"told Fox News on Monday","depth":8},{"id":46,"text":"that \" this is a non-story . \"","depth":7},{"id":47,"text":"\" No memos were given to the press ,","depth":10},{"id":48,"text":"and no memos were classified at the time","depth":11},{"id":49,"text":"I received them , \"","depth":11},{"id":50,"text":"Richman told Fox News ,","depth":9},{"id":51,"text":"explaining","depth":10},{"id":52,"text":"that the \" substance \" of one memo was given to the press but not the physical document .","depth":10},{"id":53,"text":"\" That was not classified at the time ,","depth":11},{"id":54,"text":"and remains unclassified , \"","depth":11},{"id":55,"text":"he said .","depth":10},{"id":56,"text":"Richman told Fox News","depth":8},{"id":57,"text":"he received four memos from Comey ,","depth":9},{"id":58,"text":"all of which were not marked .","depth":9},{"id":59,"text":"Richman questioned the White House claims .","depth":7},{"id":60,"text":"\" It ' s kind of interesting that the White House is now suggesting","depth":9},{"id":61,"text":"they ' re true , \"","depth":9},{"id":62,"text":"Richman said .","depth":8},{"id":63,"text":"Special Counsel Robert Mueller ' s office declined to comment on the ongoing investigation ,","depth":3},{"id":64,"text":"when asked about the report in The Hill .","depth":3},{"id":65,"text":"But White House Counselor Kellyanne Conway called the latest report an `` incredible bombshell ''","depth":4},{"id":66,"text":"and said Monday","depth":5},{"id":67,"text":"that Comey was at least violating FBI rules","depth":6},{"id":68,"text":"if the account is true .","depth":6},{"id":69,"text":"`` The boy scout , choir boy defense does n't hold up here","depth":6},{"id":70,"text":"because","depth":8},{"id":71,"text":"if it contains classified information ,","depth":10},{"id":72,"text":"he is apparently violating , at the very least , what all FBI members sign","depth":12},{"id":73,"text":"-- they sign a document","depth":13},{"id":74,"text":"saying you will not do something like this .","depth":13},{"id":75,"text":"He was the director of the entire bureau , ''","depth":11},{"id":76,"text":"Conway told `` Fox & Friends . ''","depth":9},{"id":77,"text":"`` The irony to me , anyway ... is that this is exactly the problem","depth":9},{"id":78,"text":"that Hillary Clinton had with her illegal server","depth":9},{"id":79,"text":"-- the handling of classified and confidential information","depth":9},{"id":80,"text":"that Jim Comey was meant to investigate ,","depth":10},{"id":81,"text":"if not prosecute . ''","depth":10},{"id":82,"text":"Conway added","depth":6},{"id":83,"text":"that Comey was `` admitting under oath , handing over classified information through 'private recollection '","depth":7},{"id":84,"text":"-- it does n't matter that he calls it ,","depth":8},{"id":85,"text":"it matters what it is . ''","depth":8},{"id":86,"text":"Conway recalled Comey 's testimony ,","depth":7},{"id":87,"text":"when the fired FBI director admitted leaking his notes to a close friend with the intent","depth":8},{"id":88,"text":"to trigger an appointment of a special counsel .","depth":8},{"id":89,"text":"`` If people go back","depth":9},{"id":90,"text":"and listen to him under oath ,","depth":9},{"id":91,"text":"he is admitting what his intent was , ''","depth":8},{"id":92,"text":"Conway said .","depth":7},{"id":93,"text":"`` You couple that with the fact","depth":7},{"id":94,"text":"that this was classified information ,","depth":7},{"id":95,"text":"I think","depth":7},{"id":96,"text":"this is what the story should be","depth":8},{"id":97,"text":"- not all this nonsense about Russian collusion and what not . ''","depth":8}],"relations":[{"parent":195,"left":160,"right":194,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":160,"left":124,"right":159,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":124,"left":119,"right":123,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":119,"left":116,"right":118,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":116,"left":103,"right":115,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":103,"left":0,"right":102,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":102,"left":1,"right":101,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":101,"left":100,"right":5,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":100,"left":99,"right":4,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":99,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":115,"left":110,"right":114,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":110,"left":105,"r